| # | Issue | Severity |
|---|---|---|
| 1 | No error/404 middleware; stack traces can leak | High |
| 2 | No input validation framework in place | High |
| 3 | No `helmet`, rate limiting, or body-size caps | High |
| 4 | PII (`email`) returned without auth | High |
| 5 | Hard-coded port; listens on import | Medium |
| 6 | Unstructured logging via `console` | Medium |
| 7 | No async error wrapper for future handlers | Medium |

